245
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>船井</b></font>

246
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:49,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>冷静一点</b></font>

247
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:50,740
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>到底出了什么事</b></font>

248
