292
00:17:58,090 --> 00:17:59,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他也被迫上船了吗 那家伙</b></font>

293
00:18:00,490 --> 00:18:01,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别想逃</b></font>

