<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是...</b></font>

297
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在那里却是...</b></font>

298
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:23,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>废人聚集地</b></font>

299
00:18:24,490 --> 00:18:30,960
