<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>跟我走 古畑</b></font>

304
00:18:49,340 --> 00:18:54,580
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司先生 对不起 我...对不起</b></font>

305
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:56,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别说了 跟我从这里出去</b></font>

