308
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,710
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那些家伙 并没有意识到自己的可能性</b></font>

309
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:20,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>心灵被绝望的状况所压垮</b></font>

310
00:19:20,670 --> 00:19:24,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>自己封闭了仅存的通向胜利的道路</b></font>

311
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:29,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但也是没办法的 一想到再输一次就会...</b></font>

