320
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:56,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>等等...</b></font>

321
00:19:57,630 --> 00:19:58,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是星星</b></font>

322
00:19:58,790 --> 00:19:59,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>星星?</b></font>

323
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:02,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>回去吧 回刚才的房间里去找</b></font>

324
00:20:02,810 --> 00:20:05,520
