337
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:07,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是要想办法三人一起弄到九颗星</b></font>

338
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:08,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是</b></font>

339
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:12,580
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>弱者们为了活下去而开始行动了</b></font>

340
