<font face="DFPSNGyoSho-W5" size="22">{\an9}深みにはまって行く</font>

344
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:35,350
<font face="DFPXingShu-B5" size="22">{\an3}越陷越深</font>

345
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:42,330
<font face="DFPSNGyoSho-W5" size="22">{\an9}どっちに転ぶんだい</font>

346
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:42,330
<font face="DFPXingShu-B5" size="22">{\an3}倒向哪邊</font>

347
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:49,500
